room_title: Escape room "Ransom" by Entrap Games in Omaha
room_description:
The last thing you remember is heading down the hallway on your way to bed before the lights went out. You’ve woken up blindfolded and handcuffed in a very odd and small cell. The kidnappers have asked for a ransom, but there is no guarantee that they'll let you go even if you pay them! It’s up to you to crawl through a series of clues in search of a quick escape before they return with your fate.
This game room requires some physical activity and may be difficult for players that are unable to kneel, crawl, or jump.
